Phase 5: Readiness Engine and Progress Dashboard

- Readiness API (/api/readiness) with domain-weighted scoring using exam blueprint weights, recency bonus, confidence score (variance-based consistency), weak domain detection (below 70% or untested), verdict (Ready/Almost Ready/Needs Preparation), exam countdown, and personalized recommendations
- Progress dashboard at /dashboard/progress with readiness score card, confidence score, study streak, exam countdown, Judy's recommendation, domain performance heatmap with color-coded progress bars, weak areas section with study links, and overall stats
- All dashboard cards now active: Study Plan (coming soon), AI Tutor, Quizzes, Progress, Weak Areas, Readiness

